{"tid":270630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會悼辭：港人有責任為內地不能發聲的人發聲","createTime":"2017-06-04T12:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T01:32:19.000Z","uid":48093,"like":6,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98049b9f5615b7c2a23a450a76e6069277ffa4a5","tid":270630,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1334144_1_L_20170604203418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1334144_1_L_20170604203418.jpg&h=a2f72e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支聯會正在維園舉辦六四事件28周年燭光悼念集會，參加者坐滿約4個足球場。<br />\n<br />\n晚會於8時開始，大會先播放一段短片，回顧六四事件經過及支聯會多年來的抗爭行動，支聯會常委與一批青年，向民主烈士紀念碑獻花，全場為死難者行三鞠躬禮，支聯會主席何俊仁其後與年輕人燃點火炬，象徵薪火相傳，堅持爭取平反六四。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會副主席鄒幸彤致悼詞時說，港人有責任為內地不能發聲的人發聲、為不能致哀的人致哀，她指目前仍未知道維園持續28年的悼念，能結出甚麼果實，但懷緬死者是本著對公義的執著，對未來的期盼，她強調維園的燭光必定繼續照亮下去。"},{"pid":"6484e09298bd77bb9ea92d8cc4f8e3e861c62cca","tid":270630,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cf959e5b131d306188190c75a4c1fdf58e0947b","tid":270630,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:54:59.000Z","msg":"責乜撚野任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10296771bdde60cacae6498e735936577e6ea588","tid":270630,"uid":39777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"13億攰那人唔做，要水深火熱既香港人發聲<br />\n痴線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03af29f9a1f0b5ac79a451598963cc977e7a6a14","tid":270630,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:06:57.000Z","msg":"咩責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82ae2818ead6d7df111c37fe66831acfcdaed43","tid":270630,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":